## Testing Forms with Attachments

```ruby
test "uploads featured image" do
  sign_in_as @user
  visit new_article_url
  
  fill_in "Title", with: "Article with Image"
  fill_in "Body", with: "Body text"
  attach_file "Featured Image", Rails.root.join("test/fixtures/files/image.jpg")
  
  click_button "Create Article"
  
  assert_text "Article created"
  assert_selector "img[src*='image.jpg']"
end
```

